<note n="0031005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0031005">餅粳＝<g ref="#CB00596">󰉔</g>秔【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0031006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0031006">天王＝王天【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0031007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0031007">却＝禦【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0031008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0031008">雹＝電【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0031009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0031009">邊＝河【三】，河邊【宮】</note>
<note n="0031010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0031010">唯＝惟【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0031011" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0031011">亡＝忘【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0031012" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0031012">可＝有【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0031013" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0031013">少耳曰少＝少少耳曰【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0031014" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0031014">爾＝耳【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0031015" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0031015">（多）＋聞【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0031016" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0031016">并＝併【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0031017" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0031017">割＝別【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0031018" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0031018">經乃至事二十四字宋元明宮四本俱作本文</note>
<note n="0031019" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0031019">〔也〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0031020" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0031020">說＝論【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0032001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0032001">契＋（經）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0032002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0032002">議＝義【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0032003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0032003">閡＝礙【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0032004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0032004">一＋（一）【宋】【元】【宮】，＋（二）【明】</note>
<note n="0032005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0032005">曰＝名【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0032006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0032006">撰＝譔【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0032007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0032007">訖＝記【明】</note>
<note n="0032008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0032008">寤＝悟【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0032009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0032009">誦＝頌【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0032010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0032010">一法乃至持十五字宋元明宮四本俱作本文</note>
<note n="0032011" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0032011">阿難乃至也八字宋元明宮四本俱作本文</note>
<note n="0032012" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0032012">彌勒乃至也二十一字宋元明宮四本俱作本文</note>
<note n="0032013" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0032013">八萬四千＝四萬八千【明】</note>
<note n="0032014" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0032014">辯＝辦【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0032015" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0032015">耳＝爾【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0033001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0033001">（威）＋儀【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0033002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0033002">便＝得【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0033003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0033003">方＝劣【宮】</note>
<note n="0033004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0033004">不分卷【三】【宮】</note>
</p>
